Step-3 : calculate the area = 3.14 * radius * radius
Step-4 : print area
Step-4 : end


Sum of even number

Step-1 : start
Step-2 : declate an n,i,sum=0
Step-3 : start a loop from 0 to n for(i=0;i<=n;i+2)
Step-4 : add that into i, sum = sum+1
Step-5 :print sum
Step-6 :end
